      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Gravity Assist is an interactive physics-based minigame that lets players
    experiment with spacecraft launches and orbital mechanics inspired by NASA''s
    Psyche mission.


    Contributors

    * Bhupinder Singh * Brianna Browning
    * James Brown * Kiran Shrestha * Salem Bitney


    How to Play

    * Drag to
    aim the spacecraft launch

    * Release to launch the spacecraft

    * Adjust
    angle and speed to reach the target orbit

    * Use Reset to retry and refine
    your approach


    Tips

    * Small angle changes can greatly affect your trajectory

    *
    Start with lower power and adjust gradually

    * Change one thing at a time
    when retrying


    Acknowledgements

    * Arizona State University

    * NASA
    Psyche Mission Team

    * Cassie Bowman

'
